Base Appchains represent the next evolution in blockchain scaling, offering dedicated infrastructure without sacrificing the benefits of Base’s ecosystem. Whether you’re building a gaming platform processing millions of transactions, a DeFi protocol requiring high throughput, or an enterprise solution needing predictable costs, Appchains provide the performance and flexibility to succeed.

By combining 1-second block times, sub-cent transactions, and enterprise-grade infrastructure with seamless integration into tools like Smart Wallet and OnchainKit, Base Appchains empower developers to scale without limits. As Base continues to innovate—introducing features like Flashblocks for 200-millisecond block times and Smart Wallet Sub Accounts for simplified UX—the platform is poised to drive the global onchain economy forward.

